title: Golf-Kim, Kodaira in playoff at Hilton Head
text:
April 15, 2018 / 6:11 PM / Updated 12 hours ago Golf-Kim, Kodaira in playoff at Hilton Head Reuters Staff 1 Min Read 
April 15 (Reuters) - South Korean Kim Si-woo and Japanâ€™s Satoshi Kodaira were headed to a playoff at the RBC Heritage in South Carolina after finishing regulation tied at 12-under 272 on Sunday. 
Kim (71) bogeyed the par-three 17th to fall back into a tie with Kodaira, who was already in the clubhouse after a five-under-par 66 that also included a bogey at the penultimate hole. (Reporting by Frank Pingue in Toronto Editing by Christian Radnedge)
